{"tid":830402,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"靠父幹又如何？王子涵浮沉10年開竅","createTime":"2018-09-21T06:49:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-22T12:55:39.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"568ccd71c540bcbf21131d2818f3c89a70f499cb","tid":830402,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T06:49:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/jslyu41LI.38qOLvUmQdow--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/thesun.hk.com/d5b2c4dfe36efdb31694747690152b0b\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fjslyu41LI.38qOLvUmQdow--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fthesun.hk.com%2Fd5b2c4dfe36efdb31694747690152b0b&h=1e09bba9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ervdPtGEPyFvZh3j3TY39A--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/thesun.hk.com/1079ca707528fe475a8ffb226584aa7a\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FervdPtGEPyFvZh3j3TY39A--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fthesun.hk.com%2F1079ca707528fe475a8ffb226584aa7a&h=007801f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n藝人王子涵早年曾揚言不靠爸爸導演王晶父蔭，更有傳接拍三級片盡地一煲！惟入行10年的她坦言心態已轉變，不再執着於外界抨擊而與爸爸鬥氣，並重提當年被拍得洽談三級片一事，鬧爆有人設局陷害做新聞，澄清從沒接拍計劃！<br />\n<br />\n入行多年，王子涵（Ada）至今依然被稱為「王晶個女」，她直言最初對「靠父蔭」三個字非常反感，但現在長大了，經已看開：「好多嘢都睇化咗，靠爸爸係一條路，唔靠爸爸又係另一條路，咁當然唔係咩都要靠佢，當佢想幫而我又有需要，咁咪畀佢幫，唔使講到一定唔靠爸爸嘅！有時遇到困難又死硬頸話靠自己，只會永遠喺困局入面出唔到嚟。」<br />\n<br />\n王晶唔偏私<br />\n近年她先後參與多部由爸爸監製的劇集，包括《荷里活有個大老千》及《賭城群英會》等，她強調爸爸絕無偏私：「每次拍完場戲甚至作品出咗街，佢都會同我檢討，有次畀佢鬧得好勁，好唔開心，但嗰次真係令我喺演戲上有少少開竅，幫到我好多。」雖然她對「靠爸爸」態度軟化，但至今仍對當年被指拍三級片一事未能釋懷，她覺得有人刻意安排做新聞，但相信與該片導演劉國昌無關，並藉此機會向對方致歉。<br />\n<br />\n冇畀人催婚<br />\n即將踏入29歲，Ada表示會繼續保持童心，輕鬆面對，現時她專注事業，幸家人未有催婚，她亦明白成家立室責任重大，待有能力照顧自己時再作打算。未來她會繼續多方面發展，除了來年網店生意有新動向，亦會努力學習唱歌跳舞增值自己。"},{"pid":"d8656e6857f2941bbbd7caa7abf6e75f4b08ea90","tid":830402,"uid":35451,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T07:14:56.000Z","msg":"你對ada唔好?"},{"pid":"0f32c9d16664b20bde16b2771389421646650a72","tid":830402,"uid":146435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T07:15:19.000Z","msg":"會唔會有人氹佢指脫戲呢"},{"pid":"7f5c76a561a0c67a2dcecc31ccfd31babd5062da","tid":830402,"uid":98386,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T10:21:10.000Z","msg":"好樣衰 見過真人近睇成面雀斑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"079c7cad3b918cde8d5bb04e6478c89a780ee592","tid":830402,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T11:01:51.000Z","msg":"仲係咪處？"},{"pid":"1f7887a5473083a29c33bfa841253dea02230d7d","tid":830402,"uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7f5c76a561a0c67a2dcecc31ccfd31babd5062da","tid":830402,"uid":98386,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T10:21:10.000Z","msg":"好樣衰 見過真人近睇成面雀斑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T23:49:34.000Z","msg":"王晶d基因係咁上下啦"},{"pid":"9344fb80e62237b26fdeeab31695c9de306a72d0","tid":830402,"uid":193131,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T00:02:02.000Z","msg":"有咩所謂，佢老豆咪又係靠老豆"},{"pid":"e49f36681627bf7b5f1edb38a1a1908767cf2774","tid":830402,"uid":70988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T04:29:58.000Z","msg":"三級片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e275e6a2618803c15d3e797d8a8e3ac9cf769dbe","tid":830402,"uid":52459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T04:44:58.000Z","msg":"媽媽係邊個？"},{"pid":"2d190091b4b87c2e0b7429574e7dc38c8983eb83","tid":830402,"uid":210947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T12:55:39.000Z"